---
title: My Big Fat Greek Chicken Salad with Marinated Veggies & Feta
description: Remember that movie where the dad used Windex to fix just about everything? This salad is the equivalent of your dinner conundrums–sure to fix just about whatever needs fixin’! It all starts with a perfect marriage of crisp romaine and herby chicken, then throws in some colorful supporting characters: vinegary marinated tomatoes and shallots, fresh cucumbers, a Greek-style dressing, plus a shower of briny feta. Everyone’s sure to feel Greek when they eat this salad.
